2026-06-10T05:49:01.645225Z  INFO sqlx::query: summary="SELECT f.filename, f.storage_path, COUNT(*) …" db.statement="\n\nSELECT\n  f.filename,\n  f.storage_path,\n  COUNT(*) AS access_count,\n  COALESCE(SUM(al.bytes_transferred), 0) AS total_bytes\nFROM\n  access_log al\n  JOIN files f ON f.id = al.file_id\n  JOIN users u ON u.id = f.owner_id\nWHERE\n  u.username = $1\nGROUP BY\n  f.id,\n  f.filename,\n  f.storage_path\nORDER BY\n  access_count DESC\nLIMIT\n  $2\n" rows_affected=1 rows_returned=1 elapsed=847.622µs elapsed_secs=0.000847622
